        "timestamp": 1773623549
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Idk -- I find it encourages a longer form conversation which can be nice in an asynchronous format</p>",
        "id": 579593921,
        "sender_full_name": "Luke Boswell",
        "timestamp": 1773623580
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>yeah not one chat room for everything</p>",
